	"releaseNotes": "0.2.19: Revert 0.2.18 (valve controls and sensor normalization) — restores the previous;   stable release.\nControl-first, minimal-effort Hubitat dashboard (mDash): pick devices and go — rooms and layout are automatic. Optimized for control (not just status): bulk room/house on/off, multi-thermostat control, drag-to-dim. Installable PWA from the cloud URL. Built-in scheduler (daily/weekly/once/sunrise/sunset/mode) managed from the dashboard without Hubitat admin login. Lights, shades, thermostats, locks, HSM, scenes, hub mode, music/media, and sensors. Snapshots, favorites, and reorderable rooms/nav. Fully hosted on your hub — no Maker API or third-party cloud.",
